# Playwright / e2e scratch — accessibility-snapshot dumps and tool state.
# Pin snapshots into .snapshots/ (see PLAYWRIGHT_FLUTTER_WEB.md §4) so they
# never pollute `git status`. Committed @playwright/test specs (e2e/*.spec.ts)
# stay tracked; only generated scratch and tool output is ignored here.
.snapshots/
.playwright-cli/
.playwright-mcp/
e2e/node_modules/
e2e/test-results/
# Scratch screenshots captured during manual Playwright runs (not assertions).
e2e/*.png
